reference.title: AArch64 implementation defined register summary
reference.shortdesc: This section describes the AArch64 registers in the Cortexâ€‘A76 core that are implementation defined.

section.p: The following tables lists the AArch 64 implementation defined registers, sorted by opcode.

entry.xref: CPUACTLR_EL1, CPU Auxiliary Control Register, EL1The CPUACTLR_EL1 provides IMPLEMENTATION DEFINED configuration and control options for the core.

CPUCFR_EL1, CPU Configuration Register, EL1The CPUCFR_EL1 provides configuration information for the .
CPUECTLR_EL1, CPU Extended Control Register, EL1The CPUECTLR_EL1 provides additional IMPLEMENTATION DEFINED configuration and control options for the .
CPUPCR_EL3, CPU Private Control Register, EL3The CPUPCR_EL3 provides IMPLEMENTATION DEFINED configuration and control options for the .

ERXPFGCDN_EL1, Selected Error Pseudo Fault Generation Count Down Register, EL1Register ERXPFGCDN_EL1 accesses the ERR<n>PFGCND register for the error record selected by ERRSELR_EL1.SEL.
